						<div class="postbody">I noticed a strange bug in Mesen and Nintaco when running the game Spot.7z &lt;Spot (U) [!].nes&gt;.  From the tile screen menu, choose: Select Options.  The D-Pad or Select button should be able to move the cursor around the options menu, but they behave quite unresponsively.  I did not notice this effect in other emulators.<br /><br />Any ideas on what's special about this particular screen in this particular game regarding input?</div>

